e-mail: <promed@usa.healthnet.org>
[ProMED-mail does not ordinarily post messages about diseases that are not
considered "emerging" or "reemerging"; malaria is one of those. However,
it is clear from this message that malaria is a reemerging disease in
Bolivia. What the ecologic parameters are, what the political
considerations are, and what the solution is, cannot be answered here. If
anyone has information that is less superficial than that provided above
regarding reasons for this remarkable increase in recognized cases, please
let us know. If you have an axe to grind, grind it somewhere else. - Mod.CHC
